  Technical Support,"
        Technical Support        

Fox Software offers technical support for FoxPro 2.0.  The best way to get your technical support questions answered is on our CompuServe forum (FOXFORUM).  Thousands of professional software developers are forum members and you can tap into an unmatched pool of technical expertise to help solve your problems or answer your questions.  Included with FoxPro 2.0 is a free introductory CompuServe membership.  Please see the help topic on CompuServe -- The Fox Forum for more information.

If you do not have a CompuServe account, you can call Fox Software directly at 419-874-0162 (Monday through Friday, 8:30 A.M. to 5:00 P.M. EST/EDT) and speak with one of our Technical Support Representatives.  Please have your serial number ready when you call.  You can also send us mail at 134 W. South Boundary, Perrysburg, Ohio 43551, or send us a FAX at 419-874-4358.



See Also:    CompuServe -- The Fox Forum

