SET STICKY,"
           SET STICKY            

SET STICKY ON | OFF


Specifies display of System menu popups.
Default value - ON


When you SET STICKY ON and select a menu pad with the mouse, popup will remain on screen until you choose an option, press the Escape key or click outside of the popup.  If you SET STICKY OFF and select a system menu pad with the mouse, popup will only remain on screen while the mouse button is pressed.



