The following topics include information on the FoxPro interface.  These topics describe how to manipulate the FoxPro interface, and are displayed when you use FoxPro's context sensitive help.  To receive context sensitive help on a system window or dialog, press F1 or Alt+click when the window or dialog is frontmost.  

For additional information about the FoxPro interface, see the FoxPro Interface manual.",General in di wi me
 1-To-Many,"
