In this dialog you select a mathematical operation to create a computed field.  The options in this dialog are:

() Nothing
	No computations made on variable.

( ) Count
	Counts number of times variable exists.

( ) Sum
	Computes additive sum of values of variable.

( ) Average
	Computes arithmetic mean (average) of variable values.

( ) Lowest
	Lowest value that occurred in variable is displayed.

( ) Highest
	Highest value that occurred in variable is displayed.

( ) Std. Deviation
	Returns square root of variance for the variable values.

( ) Variance
	Statistical calculation that measures degree to which an individual field value varies from the average of all the values.


  Reset   

	Select point at which calculate operation for field is set to zero.  Displays End of Report, End of Page and any defined groups. 



