Generating Code
	When a Menu Design window is active, the Generate... option in the Program menu popup is enabled.  Choosing Generate... brings forward the Generate Menu dialog.



See Also:  Character, Comment Options, Expression Builder, General Options, Generate Menu, Menu Options, Menu Shortcut, Prompt Options, Try It 

