[ ] Page eject after printing
	When checked, sends form feed to printer after report is finished printing.

[ ] Plain page 
	When checked, suppresses printing of page headers.

[ ] Summary report 
	When checked, suppresses printing of detail lines in report.
	
[ ] Suppress blank lines 
	When checked, lines in the Detail band of the report that contain only blank fields are removed from the report. 

[ ] Add Alias
	When checked, adds an alias to expressions created in reports.



See Also:  Page Layout, Page Preview, Report Writer

