 Report Expression,"
       Report Expression         
                                   
This dialog allows you to define a field expression for a report.

This dialog contains these options:

< Expr... > 
	Enter field expression or choose Expr... to display Expression Builder to create expression.

< Format > 
	Enter format option or choose Format to display Format dialog.

[ ] Style...
	Displays Style dialog.  When checked, a style has been specified.
	
[ ] Calculate...
	Displays Calculate Field dialog.  When checked, a field has been chosen.
	
[ ] Comment...
	Displays Comment dialog.  When checked, a comment has been added.
	
[ ] Suppress...
	Displays Suppress Repeated Values dialog.
	
[ ] Stretch Vertically
	When checked, band stretches vertically to hold all data in field.  This is useful when data in a field varies in size (memo fields).

[ ] Float as Band Stretches
	When checked, causes field to be printed in specified column but on line following last line of data in vertically stretched band.



See Also:  Calculate Field, Comment, Expression Builder, Format, Report Writer, Style

