 Report Variables,"
         Report Variables        

Choose Variables from Report menu popup to display Report Variables dialog.

This dialog contains these options:

< Add >
	Displays Variable Definition dialog to create new variable.

< Change >
	Displays Variable Definition dialog to edit selected variable.  

< Delete >
	Deletes selected variable.
	
Variables (List)
	Displays variables in order evaluated.

	To change the order of items in a list with double-headed arrows (), press Tab until the item you wish to move is selected.  Press Ctrl+PgUp or Ctrl+PgDn to move the item up or down in the list.

