",Interface di me
 Report Writer,"
          Report Writer          

Create Object
	Position cursor, select desired object type from menu.

Move Among Objects
	Click on each object, or press Tab or Shift+Tab.

Select Object
	Click on object or position cursor on object and press Spacebar.

Select Multiple Objects
	Shift+click or Shift+Spacebar on desired objects.  Point outside of objects, drag around desired objects, release mouse button, or press Spacebar outside of objects, use arrow keys, press Enter when surrounded.

Deselect Object
	Shift+click or Shift+Spacebar on object.

Deselect All Objects
	Click or press Spacebar outside of objects.

Move Object
	Click on object and drag, or select object, move with arrow keys, press Enter.

Resize Object
	Ctrl+click and drag object, or Ctrl+Spacebar on object, resize with arrow keys, press Enter.

Modify Object
	Double-click on object, or position on object and press Enter.

Edit Text Object
	Ctrl+Spacebar on object, edit, press Enter when done.


           Band Types            

Title band
	Contains information that appears before main report.

Page Header band
	Displayed at top of each page of main report.

Group Header band
	Displayed at top of each data group.

Report Body band
	Makes up report body and usually contains field information from selected database(s).

Group Footer band
	Displayed at bottom of each data group.

Page Footer band
	Displayed at bottom of each page of main report.

Summary band
	One or more pages that appear after main report.


          Report Menu            

Page Layout...
	Displays Page Layout dialog.  

Page Preview...
	Displays Page Preview window that shows an accurate representation of report, including text, fields, lines and boxes.

Data Grouping...
	Displays Data Grouping dialog.

Title/Summary...
	Displays Title/Summary dialog.

Variables...
	Displays Report Variables dialog.

Box
	Allows you to draw a box or line in the Screen Design window.

Field
	Displays Report Expression dialog.

Text
	Allows you to create and edit text object.

Add Line/Remove Line
	Changes size of any band. 
	
Bring to Front/Send to Back
	Changes stacking order (front to back) of objects.  Also changes numerical order of objects, thereby changing the access order in the generated screen.  

Center
	Centers an object at center of page.

Quick Report...
	Displays Quick Report dialog.



